                        2. Fridreichs des Dietrams</rs>, 3. <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_mosprunner_QGW_II_I_1096"><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"><add>Wiener Bürger</add></roleName> Hannsen des
                  Mosprunner</rs>.</rs></rs>
